Now you tell me,
what do you want?

531
00:31:03,328 --> 00:31:04,317
你们总算来了
There you are.

532
00:31:04,495 --> 00:31:06,895
看来你找到我们迷途的羔羊了
I see you found our wandering stray.

533
00:31:07,165 --> 00:31:08,496
