Especially when it comes from her.

556
00:32:15,800 --> 00:32:17,495
少装出一副愤慨的样子
ELlJAH:
Spare me your indignation.

557
00:32:17,669 --> 00:32:19,569
你什么时候对海莉和她的孩子
When have you ever demonstrated
any kind of concern

558
