my parting gift to you both.

582
00:34:08,479 --> 00:34:09,844
结束了
That's it.

583
00:34:11,082 --> 00:34:12,674
你自由了
You're free.

584
00:34:19,824 --> 00:34:22,657
你说得没错，我能感觉到
You're right.
I can feel it.

585
00:34:23,728 --> 00:34:25,423
之前我总是想着
Before, I was always thinking about

586
00:34:25,596 --> 00:34:27,223
克劳斯会想要我做什么
what Klaus would want me to do.

587
00:34:27,398 --> 00:34:31,425
现在我想的是“去他的
