你不必帮我
You don't have to help.

605
00:35:43,441 --> 00:35:46,569
我能自己翻找这堆狼人古董
I can dig through
the werewolf antique show on my own.

606
00:35:48,112 --> 00:35:50,376
还有，你不用涂点药膏
Besides, shouldn't
you put some kind

