of ointment or
something on that?

608
00:35:53,117 --> 00:35:55,017
那咬伤杀不了我
The bite won't kill me.

609
00:35:56,387 --> 00:35:57,911
这咬伤就像尼克劳斯一样
Like Niklaus himself,
it's more of a nuisance

610
00:35:58,089 --> 00:35:59,249
顶多算是个无法赶走的麻烦
