And thanks, by the way,
for staying out here.

614
00:36:09,734 --> 00:36:10,962
你不必那样做的
You didn't have to.

615
00:36:11,135 --> 00:36:12,625
我知道
I know.

616
00:36:14,338 --> 00:36:17,364
