I can relate.

619
00:36:26,617 --> 00:36:28,141
你在想克劳斯
You're thinking about Klaus.

620
00:36:30,888 --> 00:36:33,254
也许是我太想给他扣上罪名了
Perhaps I was too willing
to condemn him.

621
00:36:34,859 --> 00:36:36,759
在我们一起的这一千年里
In the 1,000 years
that we have been together,

622
00:36:36,928 --> 00:36:39,920
我弟弟犯下了许多令人发指的罪行
my brother has committed
numerous unspeakable acts,

623
