Is he plotting against me?

674
00:40:19,683 --> 00:40:22,777
我可怜的哥哥，太多疑了
My poor brother, so paranoid.

675
00:40:24,688 --> 00:40:26,383
马赛尔什么都不知道
Marcel knows nothing.

676
00:40:27,057 --> 00:40:28,888
